            KGF part 1
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Year:</strong> 2018</li>
                <li><strong>Main Actors:</strong> yash,shrinidhi shetty,mouni roy,anant nag,achyuth kumar and more</li>
                <li><strong>Description:</strong>KGF, or Kolar Gold Fields, is an Indian film series that primarily follows the life of Rocky, portrayed by Yash. Set against the backdrop of the gold mining region in Kolar, the story unfolds in two parts.

                    In part 1, Rocky rises from humble beginnings in Mumbai to become a feared gangster in the gold mining underworld. His ambition is to rule the KGF, a place notorious for its harsh conditions and brutal regime. He confronts various adversaries, including the oppressive forces of the local mafia and corrupt politicians. </li>
