            <ul>
                <li><strong>Year:</strong> 2024</li>
                <li><strong>Main Actors:</strong> vicky kaushal,mohit raina,yami gautam,keerti kulhari and more</li>
                <li><strong>Description:</strong>The movie "Uri: The Surgical Strike" is based on true events that took place in 2016. It follows the story of an Indian army surgical strike against militant launch pads in Pakistan following a terrorist attack on an Indian army base in Uri, Kashmir. The film highlights the planning and execution of the strike by Indian special forces and features themes of patriotism, sacrifice, and the complexities of military operations. </li>
